          "notes": [
            "Use new sealing washers. Do not re-use old ones. Torque: Inlet = 32 - 37 N\u00b7m (3.3 - 3.8 kg-m, 24 - 28 ft-lb), Outlet = 35 - 43 N\u00b7m (3.6 - 4.4 kg-m, 26 - 32 ft-lb)",
